name: Last City
description:
After the depression felt in 2020, while we were distracted by the Metaverse, war broke out in the West. I don't know exactly how much time passed, I don't know how we got here. I only know that all those who survived are in one city, the last city.

I want to believe that we will make it, we will survive, I have faith in the humanity that is left.

I am survivor 77 and this is my diary.
